_:N18a0f827e1a0428dba0cbe44ac5af044 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Felicity Buchan was Parliamentary Under Secretary of State in the Department for Levelling Up, Housing and Communities between 30 October 2022 and 5 July 2024.</p>\n\n<p>She was previously Exchequer Secretary to the Treasury between 7 September 2022 and 28 October 2022.</p>\n" .
